ACADEMIC RESEARCH NOTICE:

This software is developed as part of a Bachelor of Science in Software 
Engineering research project at African Leadership University, supervised 
by Neza David Tuyishimire.

Research Title: "AGRITRACE: Blockchain-Based Traceability for Biofortified Crops"

The software is designed to support agricultural traceability and food security
initiatives in Rwanda and may be used for academic, research, and humanitarian
purposes in accordance with the ethical guidelines outlined in the project
documentation.

For research collaboration or commercial use inquiries, please contact:
- Email: contact@agritrace.rw
- Institution: African Leadership University
